org.anchoranalysis.core.index.bounded

Interface BoundedRangeIncomplete

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BoundedRange
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BoundedIndexContainer<T>, BoundedRangeIncompleteDynamic, IncompleteElementRange
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BoundedIndexContainerBridge, BoundedIndexContainerBridgeWithIndex, BoundedIndexContainerBridgeWithoutIndex, BoundedIndexContainerFromList, BoundsFromRange, IntegerSequenceContaner, SingleContainer

    public interface BoundedRangeIncomplete
extends BoundedRange
    A range of discrete integers that is not complete (missing many integers).

    It can be navigated to find where indexes are with nextIndex(int), previousIndex(int) ec.

    Author:
    Owen Feehan
